{"iti56:0.1":"Itivuttaka 56 ","iti56:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti56:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","iti56:0.4":"Pathamaasavasutta ","iti56:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti56:2.1":"“Tayome, bhikkhave, asava. ","iti56:2.2":"Katame tayo? ","iti56:2.3":"Kamasavo, bhavasavo, avijjasavo—","iti56:2.4":"ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo asava”ti. ","iti56:2.5":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti56:2.6":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti56:3.1":"“Samahito sampajano, ","iti56:3.2":"sato buddhassa savako; ","iti56:3.3":"Asave ca pajanati, ","iti56:3.4":"asavananca sambhavam. ","iti56:4.1":"Yattha ceta nirujjhanti, ","iti56:4.2":"magganca khayagaminam; ","iti56:4.3":"Asavanam khaya bhikkhu, ","iti56:4.4":"nicchato parinibbuto”ti. ","iti56:5.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti56:5.2":"Sattamam. "}